pageContext.claim: “I've been under investigation by sleaze, and they found nothing. They found nothing.”
pageContext.analysis: The issues raised by Trump's phone call with the Ukrainian president are serious. Trump now tosses that inquiry into his grievances over the Russian probe, which ended up documenting serious potential cases of obstruction of justice. Impeachment is not overturning a election nor is it a coup -- if a president is removed, the vice president would be first in line to assume the presidency -- but is part of the Constitution.
